author: Eliot Shorr-Parks | NJ Advance Media for NJ.com
title: If Jeremy Maclin is cut by Kansas City Chiefs, could he return to Eagles?
text: The Eagles signing players that used to suit up for them has been a constant theme so far this offseason, as they have been linked to receiver DeSean Jackson and even running back LeSean McCoy.
